These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: australian, french, pakistani, italian
1. Nationality:french is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:italian is between Nationality:australian and Nationality:french##2
3. Nationality:italian is on the right of Nationality:australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | australian | italian | french | pakistani |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: pepper, lettuce, lime, raspberry
1. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:raspberry##1
2. Food:lettuce is in an odd position##4
3. Food:lettuce is on the left or right of Food:pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | lettuce | pepper | raspberry | lime |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: horror, romance, adventure, comedy
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
2. Movie-Genre:horror is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:adventure is between Movie-Genre:comedy and Movie-Genre:romance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy | adventure | romance |

 #################################
 
