.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: cherry, radish, watermelon, mango
1. Food:radish == Food:radish##1
2. Food:mango is on the left or right of Food:watermelon##3
3. Food:watermelon is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:cherry is in an even position##4
5. Food:mango is on the left of Food:radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango | radish | cherry |

